  "texts": [
    "First, in Sect. 2, the taxonomy used in the review is presented and the main issues related to iVR environments, biosensors, fields of application of the iVR experiences, and the post-assessment objectives.",
    "Then, the methodology followed in the survey is described in Sect. 3.",
    "A statistical analysis forms the basis of Sect. 4 where the results of this analysis are presented in four sub-sections:",
    "(1) demographics, so as to give a general view of research time evolution, fields of application, and the main types of wearable biosensors; (2) development of the iVR environment, considering the HMD in use, the game engine, and the interaction level; (3) the experience design, focused on sample size, the control experience and the structure of the evaluation methods; and (4) the biofeedback-based iVR applications, considering how biofeedback is used, how they are designed and the conclusions that researchers may draw from these works.",
    "The good practices identified in the results of each final sector are summarized in Sect. 5."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}